00:09:01,942 --> 00:09:03,243
OH, NO.

233
00:09:05,145 --> 00:09:06,847
I-I MEAN, YES.

234
00:09:06,880 --> 00:09:08,782
OR, ACTUALLY, KIND OF.

235
00:09:08,816 --> 00:09:10,150
YOU SEE...

236
00:09:10,183 --> 00:09:12,753
IT'S NOT SO MUCH
THE GRAND GALLOPING GALA

237
00:09:12,786 --> 00:09:15,255
AS IT IS THE WONDROUS
PRIVATE GATED GARDEN

238
00:09:15,288 --> 00:09:16,456
THAT SURROUNDS THE DANCE.

239
00:09:16,489 --> 00:09:21,094
THE FLOWERS ARE SAID TO BE
THE MOST BEAUTIFUL AND FRAGRANT

240
00:09:21,128 --> 00:09:22,763
IN ALL OF EQUESTRIA.

241
00:09:22,796 --> 00:09:24,865
FOR THE NIGHT OF THE GALA
AND THAT NIGHT ALONE

242
00:09:24,898 --> 00:09:26,700
WILL THEY ALL BE IN BLOOM.

243
00:09:26,734 --> 00:09:28,368
AND THAT'S JUST THE FLORA!

244
00:09:28,401 --> 00:09:31,004
DON'T GET ME STARTED
ON THE FAUNA.

245
00:09:31,038 --> 00:09:34,274
THERE'S LOONS AND TOUCANS
AND BITTERNS, OH, MY!

246
00:09:34,307 --> 00:09:36,644
HUMMINGBIRDS
THAT CAN REALLY HUM

247
00:09:36,677 --> 00:09:38,746
AND BUZZARDS
THAT CAN REALLY BUZZ!

248
00:09:38,779 --> 00:09:41,749
BLUE JAYS AND RED JAYS
AND GREEN JAYS,

249
00:09:41,782 --> 00:09:44,084
PINK JAYS AND PINK FLAMINGOES.

250
00:09:44,117 --> 00:09:45,953
[ SQUAWKS ]

251
00:09:45,986 --> 00:09:48,822
GEE, FLUTTERSHY,
IT SOUNDS...

252
00:09:48,856 --> 00:09:49,923
BEAUTIFUL?

253
00:09:49,957 --> 00:09:51,659
Rainbow Dash:
WAIT JUST A MINUTE!

254
00:09:51,659 --> 00:09:54,227
RAINBOW DASH!
WERE YOU FOLLOWING ME?

255
00:09:54,261 --> 00:09:55,729
NO. I MEAN, YES.

256
00:09:55,763 --> 00:09:56,897
I MEAN, MAYBE.

257
00:09:56,930 --> 00:09:57,898
LOOK,
IT DOESN'T MATTER.

258
00:09:57,931 --> 00:10:00,100
I COULDN'T RISK
A GOODY-FOUR-SHOES LIKE YOU

259
00:10:00,133 --> 00:10:02,002
GIVING THAT TICKET AWAY
TO JUST ANYBODY!

260
00:10:02,035 --> 00:10:03,971
WAIT JUST ANOTHER MINUTE.

261
00:10:04,004 --> 00:10:06,406
APPLEJACK?
WERE YOU FOLLOWING ME, TOO?

262
00:10:06,439 --> 00:10:09,877
NO, I WAS FOLLOWING
THIS ONE

263
00:10:09,910 --> 00:10:12,279
TO MAKE SURE SHE DIDN'T
TRY ANY FUNNY BUSINESS.

264
00:10:12,312 --> 00:10:14,147
STILL TRYING
TO TAKE MY TICKET.

265
00:10:14,181 --> 00:10:15,282
YOUR TICKET?!

266
00:10:15,315 --> 00:10:17,384
BUT TWILIGHT'S
TAKING ME!

267
00:10:17,417 --> 00:10:19,619
[ ALL ARGUING INDISTINCTLY ]

268
00:10:26,459 --> 00:10:29,062
[ ALL ARGUING INDISTINCTLY ]

269
00:10:30,330 --> 00:10:32,800
QUIET!!

270
00:10:32,833 --> 00:10:36,236
AND THEN I SAID, "OATMEAL?
ARE YOU CRAZ--"

271
00:10:36,269 --> 00:10:37,771
OH.

272
00:10:37,805 --> 00:10:39,940
GIRLS, THERE'S NO USE
IN ARGUING.

273
00:10:39,973 --> 00:10:40,974
BUT, TWILIGHT!

274
00:10:41,008 --> 00:10:43,043
EH!
THIS IS MY DECISION.

275
00:10:43,076 --> 00:10:44,778
AND I'M GONNA MAKE IT
ON MY OWN.

276
00:10:44,812 --> 00:10:47,314
AND I CERTAINLY CAN'T THINK
STRAIGHT WITH ALL THIS NOISE.

277
00:10:47,347 --> 00:10:48,749
[ STOMACH GRUMBLING ]

278
00:10:48,782 --> 00:10:49,983
NOT TO MENTION HUNGER.

279
00:10:50,017 --> 00:10:51,451
NOW GO ON!
SHOO!

280
00:10:51,484 --> 00:10:55,422
[ ALL GRUMBLING ]

281
00:10:55,455 --> 00:10:58,759
AND DON'T WORRY!
I'LL FIGURE THIS OUT!

282
00:10:59,927 --> 00:11:01,061
SOMEHOW.

283
00:11:04,197 --> 00:11:06,734
AW, SPIKE,
WHAT AM I GONNA DO?

284
00:11:06,734 --> 00:11:09,402
ALL FIVE OF MY BEST FRIENDS
HAVE REALLY GOOD REASONS

285
00:11:09,436 --> 00:11:11,038
TO GO TO THE GALA.

286
00:11:11,071 --> 00:11:13,340
APPLEJACK
OR RAINBOW DASH?

287
00:11:13,373 --> 00:11:16,243
PINKIE PIE OR FLUTTERSHY?
RARITY?

288
00:11:16,276 --> 00:11:18,846
OH, WHO SHOULD
GO WITH ME?

289
00:11:18,879 --> 00:11:20,748
[ STOMACH GRUMBLING ]

290
00:11:20,748 --> 00:11:22,850
Waiter:
HAVE YOU MADE YOUR DECISION?

291
00:11:22,883 --> 00:11:24,818
I CAN'T DECIDE!

292
00:11:24,852 --> 00:11:27,154
TWILIGHT, HE JUST WANTS
TO TAKE YOUR ORDER.

293
00:11:27,187 --> 00:11:28,121
OH.

294
00:11:28,155 --> 00:11:31,158
I WOULD LOVE
A DAFFODIL-AND-DAISY SANDWICH.

295
00:11:31,191 --> 00:11:33,060
DO YOU HAVE
ANY RUBIES?

296
00:11:33,093 --> 00:11:34,227
NO?

297
00:11:34,261 --> 00:11:36,764
OKAY.
I'LL HAVE THE HAY FRIES.

298
00:11:36,764 --> 00:11:37,798
EXTRA CRISPY!

299
00:11:37,831 --> 00:11:39,166
WHAT DO YOU THINK,
SPIKE?

300
00:11:39,199 --> 00:11:41,268
I THINK WE HAVE TO TRY
ANOTHER RESTAURANT.

301
00:11:41,301 --> 00:11:43,036
I MEAN,
I LIKE GRASS JUST FINE,

302
00:11:43,070 --> 00:11:45,505
BUT WOULD IT HURT ANYBODY
TO OFFER SOME GEMSTONES?

303
00:11:45,538 --> 00:11:48,441
I MEAN ABOUT THE GALA AND THE
TICKET AND WHO I SHOULD TAKE.

304
00:11:48,475 --> 00:11:50,878
OH.
YOU'RE STILL ON THAT?

305
00:11:50,911 --> 00:11:52,079
SPIKE, LISTEN!

306
00:11:52,112 --> 00:11:53,380
HOW DO I CHOOSE?

307
00:11:53,413 --> 00:11:54,414
AND WHEN I DO CHOOSE,

308
00:11:54,447 --> 00:11:56,183
WILL THE OTHER FOUR
BE MAD AT ME?

309
00:11:56,216 --> 00:11:58,451
I MEAN, I COULD GIVE UP
MY TICKET AND GIVE AWAY TWO,

310
00:11:58,485 --> 00:12:00,954
BUT THAT WOULD STILL LEAVE
THREE DISAPPOINTED PONIES.

311
00:12:00,988 --> 00:12:03,023
WHAT IF I --
AH, YOUR FOOD.

312
00:12:03,056 --> 00:12:05,793
OH, THANK YOU.
THIS LOOKS SO GOOD.

313
00:12:05,826 --> 00:12:08,796
I'M SURE EVERYTHING WILL BE
MUCH CLEARER ONCE I EAT.

314
00:12:11,131 --> 00:12:12,432
UM, MADAM?

315
00:12:12,465 --> 00:12:15,435
ARE YOU GOING TO EAT YOUR FOOD
IN THE RAIN?

316
00:12:15,468 --> 00:12:16,837
IT'S NOT RAINING.

317
00:12:16,870 --> 00:12:19,506
[ THUNDER RUMBLES ]

318
00:12:19,539 --> 00:12:21,374
WHAT'S GOING ON?

319
00:12:21,408 --> 00:12:23,911
HI, THERE, BEST FRIEND FOREVER
I'VE EVER, EVER HAD.

320
00:12:23,944 --> 00:12:25,445
ENJOYING
THE SUNNY WEATHER?

321
00:12:25,478 --> 00:12:28,181
RAINBOW DASH,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

322
00:12:28,215 --> 00:12:29,382
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

323
00:12:29,416 --> 00:12:30,550
I JUST SAW THE SMARTEST,

324
00:12:30,583 --> 00:12:32,820
MOST GENEROUS PONY
ABOUT TO GET RAINED ON,

325
00:12:32,820 --> 00:12:34,888
SO I THOUGHT
I'D KICK A HOLE IN THE CLOUDS

326
00:12:34,922 --> 00:12:37,390
TO KEEP HER DRY SO SHE COULD
DINE IN PEACE, THAT'S ALL.

327
00:12:37,424 --> 00:12:40,527
RAINBOW, YOU'RE NOT TRYING
TO GET EXTRA CONSIDERATION

328
00:12:40,560 --> 00:12:41,962
FOR THE EXTRA TICKET

329
00:12:41,995 --> 00:12:44,431
BY DOING ME EXTRA-SPECIAL
FAVORS, ARE YOU?

330
00:12:44,464 --> 00:12:46,233
ME? NO, NO, NO.

331
00:12:46,266 --> 00:12:49,036
OF COURSE NOT.
UH-HUH.

332
00:12:49,069 --> 00:12:51,839
SERIOUSLY,
I'D DO IT FOR ANYPONY.

333
00:12:54,607 --> 00:12:57,110
[ GULPS,
LAUGHS NERVOUSLY ]

334
00:12:57,144 --> 00:13:00,347
RAINBOW, I AM NOT COMFORTABLE
ACCEPTING UNWANTED FAVORS,

335
00:13:00,380 --> 00:13:01,414
SO I'D APPRECIATE IT

336
00:13:01,448 --> 00:13:03,150
IF YOU'D CLOSE UP
THAT RAIN CLOUD RIGHT NOW.

337
00:13:03,183 --> 00:13:05,018
UGH! FINE!

338
00:13:05,052 --> 00:13:06,920
[ ZIP! ]

339
00:13:06,954 --> 00:13:08,321
THAT'S BETTER.

340
00:13:11,959 --> 00:13:13,060
[ GROANS ]

341
00:13:15,162 --> 00:13:17,364
TWILIGHT!
IT'S RAINING.

342
00:13:17,397 --> 00:13:19,466
NO, REALLY?

343
00:13:19,499 --> 00:13:22,069
COME WITH ME
BEFORE YOU CATCH A COLD!

344
00:13:23,904 --> 00:13:26,539
[ WHIFFLE! WHIFFLE! WHIFFLE! ]

345
00:13:26,573 --> 00:13:28,575
[ LAUGHS NERVOUSLY ]
OOPS.

346
00:13:28,608 --> 00:13:30,043
SORRY.

347
00:13:30,077 --> 00:13:31,378
OH, NO!

348
00:13:31,411 --> 00:13:33,446
IT'S QUITE ALL RIGHT!

349
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:38,018
AFTER ALL, WE ARE THE BEST
OF FRIENDS, ARE WE NOT?

350
00:13:38,051 --> 00:13:40,954
AND YOU KNOW WHAT
THE BEST OF FRIENDS DO.

351
00:13:40,988 --> 00:13:42,055
UH...

352
00:13:42,089 --> 00:13:44,057
MAKEOVER!

353
00:13:44,091 --> 00:13:45,192
[ GRUNTING ]

354
00:13:45,225 --> 00:13:46,593
RARITY! OW!

355
00:13:46,626 --> 00:13:48,195
THIS REALLY
ISN'T NECESSARY.

356
00:13:48,228 --> 00:13:50,430
I MEAN, THANK YOU, BUT --
OOH!

357
00:13:50,463 --> 00:13:51,631
THAT'S TOO TIGHT!

358
00:13:51,664 --> 00:13:53,934
[ HARP MUSIC PLAYS ]

359
00:13:53,967 --> 00:13:56,603
THERE!
OH, YOU'RE SIMPLY DARLING!

360
00:13:56,636 --> 00:13:58,038
UH...

361
00:13:58,071 --> 00:14:00,340
YEAH, IT IS KIND OF PRETTY,
ISN'T IT?

362
00:14:00,373 --> 00:14:02,475
AND YOU!

363
00:14:02,509 --> 00:14:05,078
OH, SPIKE, I HAVE
A DANDY LITTLE OUTFIT

364
00:14:05,112 --> 00:14:06,346
FOR THE DASHING GENT.

365
00:14:06,379 --> 00:14:10,283
WHOA! OUCH! OH! HEY!
COME ON! WATCH IT! WHOA!

366
00:14:10,317 --> 00:14:13,353
[ HARPSICHORD MUSIC PLAYS ]

367
00:14:13,386 --> 00:14:16,223
OH, SPIKE.
NOW YOU JUST NEED A HAT.

368
00:14:16,256 --> 00:14:17,457
UGH!

369
00:14:17,490 --> 00:14:20,093
I TOLD YOU, I DON'T WANT ANY
PART OF THIS GIRLY GALA GUNK.

370
00:14:20,127 --> 00:14:21,628
SEE YOU BACK AT THE LIBRARY.
[ ZIP! ]

371
00:14:21,661 --> 00:14:24,564
[ LAUGHS NERVOUSLY ]
OH, WHO NEEDS HIM ANYWAY?

372
00:14:24,597 --> 00:14:25,698
THIS IS ALL ABOUT YOU

373
00:14:25,732 --> 00:14:29,436
AND HOW FABULOUS YOU'LL LOOK
AT THE GRAND GALLOPING GALA.

374
00:14:29,469 --> 00:14:30,938
WAIT.
THE GRAND --

375
00:14:30,971 --> 00:14:31,939
[ GASPS ]

376
00:14:31,939 --> 00:14:35,008
AND, OH, MY GOODNESS.
WHAT A COINCIDENCE.

377
00:14:35,042 --> 00:14:37,644
I HAPPEN TO HAVE AN ENSEMBLE
OF MY OWN

378
00:14:37,677 --> 00:14:39,980
THAT MATCHES YOURS
TO A "T."

379
00:14:40,013 --> 00:14:42,349
WE WOULD BE THE BELLES
OF THE BALL, YOU AND I.

380
00:14:42,382 --> 00:14:44,952
EVERYONE WOULD BE CLAMORING
FOR OUR ATTENTION.

381
00:14:44,952 --> 00:14:46,219
ALL EYES
WOULD BE ON US.

382
00:14:46,253 --> 00:14:48,088
AND THEN EVERYONE
WOULD FINALLY KNOW

383
00:14:48,121 --> 00:14:49,656
THE MOST BEAUTIFUL,
MOST TALENTED,

384
00:14:49,689 --> 00:14:51,959
MOST SOPHISTICATED PONY
IN ALL OF EQUESTRIA

385
00:14:51,992 --> 00:14:54,227
IS RARITY THE UNICORN!

386
00:14:56,363 --> 00:14:58,165
[ GIGGLES NERVOUSLY ]

387
00:14:58,198 --> 00:14:59,967
AND TWILIGHT SPARKLE,
OF COURSE.

388
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:01,034
[ GIGGLES NERVOUSLY ]

389
00:15:01,068 --> 00:15:02,302
I SEE WHAT'S GOING ON.

390
00:15:02,335 --> 00:15:04,972
YOU'RE JUST BUTTERING ME UP
SO I GIVE YOU THE EXTRA TICKET.

391
00:15:05,005 --> 00:15:06,206
WELL,
IT'S NOT GONNA WORK.

392
00:15:06,239 --> 00:15:08,208
YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE TO WAIT
FOR MY DECISION

393
00:15:08,241 --> 00:15:09,309
JUST LIKE EVERYONE ELSE.

394
00:15:09,342 --> 00:15:10,610
NOW, IF YOU'LL EXCUSE ME,

395
00:15:10,643 --> 00:15:13,280
I'VE BEEN TRYING ALL DAY
JUST TO GET SOME LUNCH!

396
00:15:13,313 --> 00:15:16,049
DID SOMEPONY SAY "LUNCH"?

397
00:15:17,650 --> 00:15:19,686
YOU'VE GOT
TO BE KIDDING ME!

398
00:15:19,719 --> 00:15:22,455
I GOT APPLE PIE,
APPLE FRITTERS, APPLE TARTS,

399
00:15:22,489 --> 00:15:24,624
APPLE DUMPLINGS,
APPLE CRISP, APPLE CRUMBLERS,

400
00:15:24,657 --> 00:15:27,627
AND APPLE BROWN BETTY!

401
00:15:27,660 --> 00:15:30,163
UH, THE DESSERT,
NOT MY AUNTIE.

402
00:15:30,197 --> 00:15:32,199
WHAT DO YOU SAY THERE,
BEST FRIEND?

403
00:15:32,232 --> 00:15:33,733
[ STOMACH GRUMBLING ]

404
00:15:33,766 --> 00:15:36,469
IS THAT A "YES"?

405
00:15:36,503 --> 00:15:38,205
NO. NO!

406
00:15:38,238 --> 00:15:40,340
I DON'T KNOW
WHO I'M GIVING THE TICKET TO!

407
00:15:40,373 --> 00:15:43,243
AND ALL THESE FAVORS AREN'T
MAKING IT ANY EASIER TO DECIDE.

408
00:15:43,276 --> 00:15:46,413
IN FACT, I'M LESS SURE NOW
THAN I WAS THIS MORNING!

409
00:15:46,446 --> 00:15:47,747
UGH!

410
00:15:47,780 --> 00:15:50,383
SO, THAT'S A "MAYBE"?

411
00:15:54,487 --> 00:15:55,388
[ SIGHS ]

412
00:15:55,422 --> 00:15:57,357
I NEVER THOUGHT
BEING SHOWERED WITH FAVORS

413
00:15:57,390 --> 00:15:58,558
WOULD BE SO AGGRAVATING!

414
00:15:58,591 --> 00:16:01,161
[ HUMMING ]

415
00:16:05,198 --> 00:16:08,335
[ GASPS ]
FLUTTERSHY! NOT YOU, TOO!

416
00:16:08,368 --> 00:16:10,270
OH!
WELL, HELLO, TWILIGHT.

417
00:16:10,303 --> 00:16:11,638
I HOPE YOU DON'T MIND,

418
00:16:11,671 --> 00:16:14,441
BUT WE'RE ALL DOING A LITTLE
SPRING CLEANING FOR YOU.

419
00:16:14,474 --> 00:16:15,508
IT'S SUMMER.

420
00:16:15,542 --> 00:16:16,376
OH.

421
00:16:16,409 --> 00:16:19,579
WELL, BETTER LATE
THAN NEVER, RIGHT?

422
00:16:19,612 --> 00:16:21,514
IT WAS ANGEL'S IDEA.

423
00:16:21,548 --> 00:16:23,583
[ SQUEAKS ]

424
00:16:23,616 --> 00:16:26,119
YOU'RE NOT DOING THIS
FOR THE TICKET, ARE YOU?

425
00:16:26,153 --> 00:16:27,187
OH, NO!

426
00:16:27,220 --> 00:16:30,757
I'M DOING THIS BECAUSE
YOU'RE MY VERY BEST FRIEND,

427
00:16:30,790 --> 00:16:32,159
RIGHT, ANGEL?

428
00:16:32,192 --> 00:16:34,061
OH.

429
00:16:34,061 --> 00:16:37,064
YES, WE ARE JUST DOING THIS
FOR THE TICKET.

430
00:16:37,097 --> 00:16:39,299
[ STOMACH GRUMBLING ]

431
00:16:39,332 --> 00:16:41,201
NO! NO! NO!

432
00:16:41,234 --> 00:16:43,236
WELL, THIS WAS ALL
VERY NICE OF YOU AND ANGEL,

433
00:16:43,270 --> 00:16:44,804
BUT I'M NOT ACCEPTING
ANY EXTRA FAVORS

434
00:16:44,837 --> 00:16:46,473
UNTIL I'VE MADE
MY FINAL DECISION.

435
00:16:46,506 --> 00:16:48,241
SO I'M GOING TO HAVE
TO ASK YOU TO LEAVE.

436
00:16:48,275 --> 00:16:50,343
SURPRISE!
SURPRISE!
SURPRISE!
SURPRISE!

437
00:16:50,377 --> 00:16:51,144
[ HORNS BLOWING ]

438
00:16:51,178 --> 00:16:52,712
* TWILIGHT IS
MY BESTEST FRIEND *

439
00:16:52,745 --> 00:16:54,481
* WHOOPEE, WHOOPEE
PINKIE --

440
00:16:54,514 --> 00:16:57,217
* SHE'S THE CUTEST, SMARTEST,
ALL-AROUND BEST PONY, PONY *

441
00:16:57,250 --> 00:17:00,153
PINKIE --
* I BET IF I THROW
A SUPER-DUPER FUN PARTY, PARTY *

442
00:17:00,187 --> 00:17:03,290
PINKIE!
* SHE'LL GIVE HER EXTRA TICKET
TO THE GALA TO ME *

443
00:17:03,323 --> 00:17:07,327
PINKIE!!

444
00:17:07,360 --> 00:17:09,296
YES, TWILIGHT?

445
00:17:09,329 --> 00:17:10,563
[ BLINK! BLINK! BLINK! BLINK! ]

446
00:17:10,597 --> 00:17:12,199
AT LEAST
THE OTHER PONIES

447
00:17:12,232 --> 00:17:14,234
TRIED TO BE SUBTLE
ABOUT THE TICKET.

448
00:17:14,267 --> 00:17:16,136
WAIT, WHAT TICKET?
WHAT GALA?

449
00:17:16,169 --> 00:17:17,270
OH,
YOU DIDN'T KNOW?

450
00:17:17,304 --> 00:17:20,340
TWILIGHT HAS AN EXTRA TICKET
TO THE GRAND GALLOPING GALA!

451
00:17:20,373 --> 00:17:23,243
All:
THE GRAND GALLOPING GALA?!

452
00:17:23,276 --> 00:17:25,312
HAVE I EVER TOLD YOU
HOW MUCH I LOVE YOUR MANE?

453
00:17:25,345 --> 00:17:26,279
I'LL WASH YOUR DISHES.

454
00:17:26,313 --> 00:17:28,648
WOULD YOU LIKE ANY HELP
WITH YOUR GARDENING?

455
00:17:28,681 --> 00:17:31,118
I HAVE CARTLOAD
OF EXTRA CARROTS.

456
00:17:31,118 --> 00:17:32,719
[ ALL TALKING OVER EACH OTHER ]

457
00:17:32,752 --> 00:17:34,287
WHAT ARE WE GONNA DO?

458
00:17:34,321 --> 00:17:36,223
WE'RE...GONNA...

459
00:17:36,256 --> 00:17:38,658
RUN!

460
00:18:12,159 --> 00:18:14,394
[ ALL TALKING OVER EACH OTHER ]

461
00:18:14,427 --> 00:18:18,265
[ OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYS ]

462
00:18:19,532 --> 00:18:20,500
[ ALL GASPING ]

463
00:18:20,533 --> 00:18:22,169
WHERE IS SHE?
WHERE DID SHE GO?

464
00:18:22,202 --> 00:18:23,236
SHE'S
DISAPPEARED!

465
00:18:23,270 --> 00:18:24,804
[ POOF! ]

466
00:18:24,837 --> 00:18:26,406
[ GROANS ]

467
00:18:26,439 --> 00:18:29,342
WARN ME NEXT TIME
YOU'RE GONNA DO THAT.

468
00:18:29,376 --> 00:18:31,344
I DIDN'T EVEN KNOW
IT WAS GONNA HAPPEN.

469
00:18:31,378 --> 00:18:32,779
NOW QUICK --
LOCK THE DOORS!

470
00:18:32,812 --> 00:18:34,614
[ BLOWS ]

471
00:18:37,684 --> 00:18:39,919
WHEW.

472
00:18:39,952 --> 00:18:41,354
[ OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYS ]

473
00:18:41,388 --> 00:18:42,789
YAH!

474
00:18:42,822 --> 00:18:45,258
I CAN'T DECIDE!
I JUST CAN'T DECIDE!

475
00:18:45,292 --> 00:18:46,293
IT'S IMPORTANT TO ALL OF YOU,

476
00:18:46,326 --> 00:18:48,295
AND I JUST CAN'T STAND
TO DISAPPOINT ANY OF YOU.

477
00:18:48,328 --> 00:18:50,697
AND GIVING ME GIFTS AND DOING ME
FAVORS WON'T MAKE ANY DIFFERENCE

478
00:18:50,730 --> 00:18:52,199
BECAUSE YOU'RE ALL
MY FRIENDS,

479
00:18:52,232 --> 00:18:53,533
AND I WANT TO MAKE
YOU ALL HAPPY.

480
00:18:53,566 --> 00:18:55,902
AND I CAN'T!
I JUST CAN'T!

481
00:18:55,935 --> 00:19:00,307
TWILIGHT, SUGAR, I-I DIDN'T MEAN
TO PUT SO MUCH PRESSURE ON YOU.

482
00:19:00,340 --> 00:19:03,210
AND IF IT HELPS,
I DON'T WANT THE TICKET ANYMORE.

483
00:19:03,243 --> 00:19:05,278
YOU CAN GIVE IT
TO SOMEPONY ELSE.

484
00:19:05,312 --> 00:19:07,214
I WON'T FEEL BAD.
I PROMISE.

485
00:19:07,247 --> 00:19:08,248
ME TOO.

486
00:19:08,281 --> 00:19:11,784
I FEEL JUST AWFUL
THAT I MADE YOU FEEL SO AWFUL.

487
00:19:11,818 --> 00:19:14,854
AND ME TOO! IT'S NO FUN
UPSETTING YOUR FRIENDS.

488
00:19:14,887 --> 00:19:18,558
TWILIGHT, IT WAS UNFAIR OF ME
TO TRY TO FORCE YOU AS I DID.

489
00:19:18,591 --> 00:19:21,528
YES!
THAT MEANS THE TICKET IS MINE!

490
00:19:21,561 --> 00:19:22,562
[ LAUGHS ]

491
00:19:22,595 --> 00:19:26,299
* I'VE GOT THE TICKET,
I'VE GOT THE TICKET *

492
00:19:28,535 --> 00:19:31,538
YOU KNOW, I HAVEN'T
PERFECTED MY SIGNATURE MOVES

493
00:19:31,571 --> 00:19:33,306
FOR THE WONDERBOLTS, ANYWAY.

494
00:19:33,340 --> 00:19:35,475
I DON'T NEED THAT TICKET,
EITHER.

495
00:19:35,508 --> 00:19:38,345
WE ALL GOT SO GUNG HO
ABOUT GOING TO THE GALA

496
00:19:38,378 --> 00:19:41,681
THAT WE COULDN'T SEE HOW
UN-GUNG HO WE WERE MAKING YOU.

497
00:19:41,714 --> 00:19:43,783
Together:
WE'RE SORRY, TWILIGHT.

498
00:19:43,816 --> 00:19:45,552
SPIKE,
TAKE DOWN A NOTE.

499
00:19:45,585 --> 00:19:47,920
"DEAR PRINCESS CELESTIA,

500
00:19:47,954 --> 00:19:50,390
"I'VE LEARNED THAT ONE
OF THE JOYS OF FRIENDSHIP

501
00:19:50,423 --> 00:19:51,524
"IS SHARING YOUR BLESSINGS.

502
00:19:51,558 --> 00:19:54,261
"BUT WHEN THERE'S NOT ENOUGH
BLESSINGS TO GO AROUND,

503
00:19:54,294 --> 00:19:56,996
"HAVING MORE THAN YOUR FRIENDS
CAN MAKE YOU FEEL PRETTY AWFUL.

504
00:19:57,029 --> 00:19:59,266
"SO, THOUGH I APPRECIATE
THE INVITATION,

505
00:19:59,266 --> 00:20:02,702
I WILL BE RETURNING BOTH TICKETS
TO THE GRAND GALLOPING GALA."

506
00:20:02,735 --> 00:20:03,836
WHAT?!
WHAT?!
WHAT?!
WHAT?!

507
00:20:03,870 --> 00:20:07,740
"IF MY FRIENDS CAN'T ALL GO,
I DON'T WANT TO GO, EITHER."

508
00:20:07,774 --> 00:20:10,810
TWILIGHT, YOU DON'T
HAVE TO DO THAT.

509
00:20:10,843 --> 00:20:12,645
NOPE.
I'VE MADE UP MY MIND.

510
00:20:12,679 --> 00:20:14,781
SPIKE, YOU CAN
SEND THE LETTER NOW.

511
00:20:14,814 --> 00:20:16,516
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

512
00:20:16,549 --> 00:20:17,484
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

513
00:20:17,517 --> 00:20:20,320
NOW YOU WON'T GET TO GO
TO THE GALA, EITHER.

514
00:20:20,353 --> 00:20:21,521
IT'S OKAY, GIRLS.

515
00:20:21,554 --> 00:20:22,955
I COULDN'T POSSIBLY ENJOY MYSELF

516
00:20:22,989 --> 00:20:24,924
WITHOUT MY BEST FRIENDS
THERE WITH ME.

517
00:20:24,957 --> 00:20:25,992
[ ALL GIGGLING ]

518
00:20:26,025 --> 00:20:28,328
SO I WOULD RATHER
NOT GO AT ALL.

519
00:20:29,762 --> 00:20:31,464
[ GAGGING ]

520
00:20:31,498 --> 00:20:33,433
WELL, WALLOP
MY WITHERS, SPIKE.

521
00:20:33,466 --> 00:20:34,967
ISN'T THAT
JUST LIKE A BOY?

522
00:20:35,001 --> 00:20:37,370
CAN'T HANDLE THE LEAST BIT
OF SENTIMENT.

523
00:20:37,404 --> 00:20:39,272
[ BURPS ]
WHOA, NELLY!

524
00:20:39,306 --> 00:20:40,239
[ POOF! ]

525
00:20:40,273 --> 00:20:43,410
A LETTER FROM THE PRINCESS?
THAT WAS FAST.

526
00:20:43,443 --> 00:20:45,645
"MY FAITHFUL STUDENT
TWILIGHT,

527
00:20:45,678 --> 00:20:48,881
WHY DIDN'T YOU JUST SAY SO
IN THE FIRST PLACE?"

528
00:20:48,915 --> 00:20:51,718
SIX TICKETS
TO THE GRAND GALLOPING GALA!

529
00:20:51,751 --> 00:20:52,819
[ ALL GASPING ]

530
00:20:52,852 --> 00:20:54,687
NOW WE CAN ALL GO!

531
00:20:54,721 --> 00:20:56,789
[ ALL CHEERING ]

532
00:20:56,823 --> 00:20:58,758
[ STOMACH GRUMBLING ]

533
00:20:58,791 --> 00:21:00,593
[ LAUGHS NERVOUSLY ]

534
00:21:00,627 --> 00:21:02,529
ALLOW US
TO TREAT YOU TO DINNER.

535
00:21:02,562 --> 00:21:05,332
WHAT A GREAT WAY
TO APOLOGIZE.

536
00:21:05,332 --> 00:21:06,733
AND TO CELEBRATE!

537
00:21:06,766 --> 00:21:09,902
COME ON, EVERYONE!
THE CUPCAKES ARE ON ME!

538
00:21:12,505 --> 00:21:14,941
HOW COME I DON'T GET A TICKET
TO THE GALA?

539
00:21:14,974 --> 00:21:15,942
[ GASPS ]

540
00:21:15,975 --> 00:21:18,378
[ BURPS ]

541
00:21:18,411 --> 00:21:20,547
"AND ONE FOR YOU, SPIKE."

542
00:21:20,580 --> 00:21:24,384
[ GIGGLING ]

543
00:21:24,417 --> 00:21:26,052
I MEAN, GROSS!

544
00:21:26,085 --> 00:21:29,422
I HAVE TO GO, TOO?

545
00:21:29,456 --> 00:21:32,859
[ ZIP! ]
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

546
00:21:36,996 --> 00:21:39,466
* MY LITTLE PONY

547
00:21:41,468 --> 00:21:43,736
* MY LITTLE PONY

548
00:21:54,481 --> 00:21:56,549
* MY LITTLE PONY

549
00:21:56,583 --> 00:21:59,586
* FRIENDS

